  <h2>Text alignment</h2>

  <code>.text--left</code> 
  <code>.text--center</code> 
  <code>.text--right</code> 

  <p class="text--left">Left-aligned text</p>

  <p class="text--center">Centered text</p>

  <p class="text--right">Right-aligned text</p>
  
  <h2>Lead paragraph</h2>

  <code>.lead</code>
  
  <p class="lead">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, usu in odio gubergren conclusionemque. Eu putant reprehendunt cum, tacimates platonem per at. Deserunt consulatu cu sea, discere intellegam conclusionemque mei an, nec ex soluta alterum cotidieque. Quis nonumes delectus mei ne, eum et amet sanctus perfecto. Ad verear scripta usu.</p>

  <h2>Dropcap</h2>

  <code>.dropcap</code>
  
  <p class="deco-text-success-dark">Paraphraph with dropcap first letter, using <code>::first-letter</code>. The dropcap sits on the baseline of the third line of text.</p>
  
  <p class="dropcap">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, usu in odio gubergren conclusionemque. Eu putant reprehendunt cum, tacimates platonem per at. Deserunt consulatu cu sea, discere intellegam conclusionemque mei an, nec ex soluta alterum cotidieque. Quis nonumes delectus mei ne, eum et amet sanctus perfecto. Ad verear scripta usu. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, usu in odio gubergren conclusionemque. Eu putant reprehendunt cum, tacimates platonem per at. </p>

  <p class="deco-text-success-dark">Lead and dropcap can also be used in combination.</p>
  
  <p class="lead dropcap">Eu putant reprehendunt cum, tacimates platonem per at. Deserunt consulatu cu sea, discere intellegam conclusionemque mei an, nec ex soluta alterum cotidieque. Quis nonumes delectus mei ne, eum et amet sanctus perfecto. Ad verear scripta usu. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, usu in odio gubergren conclusionemque. Eu putant reprehendunt cum, tacimates platonem per at. </p>
  
  <h2>Initial icon</h2>
  
  <code>.initial-icon</code>
  
  <p class="deco-text-success-dark">For use in notifications, etc. Similar to dropcap, but using <code>i:first-child</code> instead of <code>::first-letter</code>. The enlgd icon spans <i>at least</i> two lines of text.</p>
  
  <p class="initial-icon"><i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, usu in odio gubergren conclusionemque.</p>
  
  <p class="deco-text-success-dark">The list of Font Awesome icons is at <a class="http://fontawesome.io/icons/" target="blank">http://fontawesome.io/icons/</a>. And add other <code>.deco-</code> classes for interesting results.</p>
  
